<h3 id="why-working-with-code-monkeys-can-be-difficult">Why Working with â€œCode Monkeysâ€ Can Be Difficult</h3>

<p>Another downside of the â€œcode monkeyâ€ mentality is that it creates a toxic work environment. Iâ€™ve heard countless stories of developers who respond to questions with grunts or, worse, completely ignore colleagues in meetings or discussions. This creates a culture of indifference and disengagement, which makes for a very difficult and unproductive workplace.</p>

