<p>The good news is that change is possible. More and more, companies are recognizing the importance of well-rounded engineers who can communicate effectively, collaborate with diverse teams, and think creatively. Weâ€™re seeing a shift toward hiring engineers who possess both technical expertise and strong interpersonal skills.</p>

